OL,3,CCardiff Council considers new parking
OL,4,Clevy for drivers and businesses
OL,6,FBusinesses who provide parking spaces
OL,7,Ffor their staff could be charged under
OL,8,Fa proposal being considered by Cardiff
OL,9,FCouncil.
OL,11,FCabinet members are meeting to discuss
OL,12,Fa new report into the development of a
OL,13,Fbusiness case for a Workplace Parking
OL,14,FLevy in the capital, with the aim of
OL,15,Fcutting congestion and improving air
OL,16,Fquality.
OL,18,FMoney raised from the scheme would be
OL,19,Fspent on public transport projects.
