OL,3,CCardiff Council considers new parking
OL,4,Clevy for drivers and businesses
OL,6,FWhile the idea was first proposed in
OL,7,F2020, the council has been developing
OL,8,Fideas for a Road User Payment Scheme
OL,9,Fsince April 2023.
OL,11,FThe council says it will decide
OL,12,Fbetween a 'Road User Payment'
OL,13,F(congestion charge) or the Workplace
OL,14,FParking Levy.
OL,16,FUnder the latter, businesses could
OL,17,Feither pay the cost themselves, or
OL,18,Fpass it on to employees who make use
OL,19,Fof spaces.
