OL,3,CCardiff Council considers new parking
OL,4,Clevy for drivers and businesses
OL,6,FNottingham is currently the only city
OL,7,Fto operate a similar scheme, although
OL,8,Fothers have considered it.
OL,10,FEmployers that provide 11 or more
OL,11,Fspaces at workplaces are charged #570
OL,12,Fper space in 2025-26.
OL,14,FSmaller employees are discounted by
OL,15,F100%, along with spaces for disabled
OL,16,Fpeople and NHS premises.
OL,18,FThe scheme, which has been in
OL,19,Foperation since 2012, helped fund an
OL,20,Fextension of Nottingham's tram network.
