OL,4,Clevy for drivers and businesses
OL,6,FCllr Dan De'Ath, Cabinet Member for
OL,7,FClimate Change, Strategic Planning and
OL,8,FTransport, said: "Road user charging
OL,9,Fcan take many forms, so we need to
OL,10,Fmake sure the option chosen is the
OL,11,Fright one for Cardiff. The city faces
OL,12,Fgrowing challenges, which we are
OL,13,Faddressing through a variety of
OL,14,Fmeasures.
