OL,3,CCardiff Council considers new parking
OL,4,Clevy for drivers and businesses
OL,6,F"We need people to be less reliant on
OL,7,Fprivate cars to reduce congestion,
OL,8,Ffurther improve air quality, and
OL,9,Finvest in public transport. To achieve
OL,10,Fthis, we must provide credible
OL,11,Falternatives, and we are committed to
OL,12,Fmaking this happen."
OL,14,F"Increased funding is needed from a
OL,15,FRoad User Payment Scheme to
OL,16,Fsignificantly improve travel choices
OL,17,Fby investing in transport schemes that
OL,18,Fencourage more walking, cycling and
OL,19,Ftravel by public transport."
