OL,6,F"The business case work is a three-
OL,7,Fstage process to develop the options
OL,8,Fto its conclusion, and as such we
OL,9,Fcannot predetermine any decision until
OL,10,Fthe final business case is completed
OL,11,Fand approved by Cabinet. However, we
OL,12,Fare keen to keep businesses and
OL,13,Fresidents updated as the process
OL,14,Fcontinues".
